{"tid":1513904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陰謀論：警察揸支槍指住特首個頭","createTime":"2019-08-28T14:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:50:59.000Z","uid":241000,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea4b7fcfcee836da72edf3c75ea4a7de238febe","tid":1513904,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"聽到樓下捉棋阿伯傾計講嘅陰謀論，好似又有啲道理 ：<br />\n<br />\n當初，示威者要求成立獨立調查委員會，<br />\n班警察就此住自己有碌炮，挾持政府，<br />\n威迫政府表態要絕對支持警察，<br />\n佢哋先肯出手做嘢，咁樣反而令到警察更加 無法無天咁，<br />\n濫捕，濫用武力，選擇性執法，所以，<br />\n政府暗中求救中共幫手解決，<br />\n港澳辦於是諗住製造假表面證據（ 恐怖主義苗頭 顏色革命）支持下，可以喺基本法框架之下，<br />\n一箭雙鵰，出解放軍取締警察，<br />\n間接廢除警察權力，警察知驚就即刻喺記者會不斷澄清，<br />\n沒有恐怖主義沒有顏色革命出現 ，<br />\n大大巴咁摑返轉頭，完全落曬港澳辦面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n可惜「外國勢力」出咗聲話唔畀中央亂咁出兵 救番佢地一命。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個廢佬講到似層層， 我都爭啲信咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a63ee3392f26c46b4819ff461ab4df99ec6219","tid":1513904,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wruJph.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wruJph.gif&h=74a08a8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b48e49585fc1ddb1c053ff4d75b04635dac386aa","tid":1513904,"uid":104044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"樓豬就係廢老"},{"pid":"378b15ecb0a87cd35dc29c8ce2cc54a495f20c2d","tid":1513904,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c66d51a8249b3bf562d884b60b3c8632b9765c","tid":1513904,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b48e49585fc1ddb1c053ff4d75b04635dac386aa","tid":1513904,"uid":104044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"